name: The Queen's Dreams: Angels of Light
description:
They were proud to be her workforce.
Here to help the progress of all souls.
From afar it looked as though they were clambering and reaching but up close the signals of their work were seen through smoke and light.
They were tirelessly feeding the energy of hope.
Up and over.
Through and round.
Knitting and weaving layer upon layer of glorious colour.
They held the key to the colours of the future.
To them this was never work.
This was their divine purpose.
